data.description: This is the one, look no further. This very well maintained 4bdrm/2bath home is move in ready. This Garfield Ridge Ranch features 3 bedrooms on the main floor with a beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, and SS appliances. The entire main floor has Hardwood floors. The basement features a large Family room, full bath and bar, perfect for entertaining. The basement also has an additional bedroom, and laundry room. The roof was recently replaced, it was a complete tear off. The basement also has a sump pump with a battery back up. The entire rear yard is paved, so no worries about cutting grass all summer. Home is close to restaurants, expressways, and schools. Easy show, make your appointments today.
